Package org.qteam.tinyicon Description

The base TinyIcon package. It provides classes for dealing with icons.

The package includes:

  • The main TinyIcon class which provides methods to load, search and sort icons.
  • The Icon entity that allows to get the associated BufferedImage.
  • Some classes that define the main two icon exceptions such as InvalidIconException and InvalidIconDataException.
  • An utility class which provides methods to read data from buffers, convert images to png and testing URLs.
